{"tid":2051590,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以唔好當我對你嘅好係奉旨","createTime":"2020-06-05T01:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T03:29:48.000Z","uid":18612,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"73ef58463cfb6e2a563bb9d6d9a1d3c5faca15c4","tid":2051590,"uid":18612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T01:54:56.000Z","msg":"我又要返兩份工又返學又整文宣已經好攰，我朋友都問點解咁傻要去安慰個陌生人，我同你本身互不相識，但同你講電話你一味重複同條女啲嘢，聽過三四次都要重複，我話我已經聽過，你又好燥咁話「你比我講埋先得唔得姐」<br />\n<br />\n我安慰你係想比你有個情緒出口，但你好似唸經咁講完一次又一次去自我陶醉，你明唔明我攤喺床攰到仆街而又要聽你重複同條女啲嘢幾辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下下講電話得你講無我講<br />\n<br />\n你係有進步，但你幾時先可以唔去諗返當初點點點，我無義務安慰你架，你可唔可以唔好當老奉啊"},{"pid":"37fc0d9e5005dd53c00e5221858597a399e20e24","tid":2051590,"uid":165665,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T01:56:22.000Z","msg":"又要安慰人 又要話人煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好地地做咩安慰人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ace6c3517b288fc8147db8193947a2f07381e05","tid":2051590,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:01:06.000Z","msg":"gay?"},{"pid":"5cceb345152bbad560073ec2b440171e43011e86","tid":2051590,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:33:47.000Z","msg":"He is chicken"},{"pid":"2ed16cee89ab7f710e8d4e95e663c37f08c4ac6b","tid":2051590,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:37:40.000Z","msg":"點解咁傻要去安慰個陌生人"},{"pid":"15d8e39cf1fa8b8ce9ebf4ec32267779e5385c2b","tid":2051590,"uid":184985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:40:40.000Z","msg":"好明啊 究竟我做緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87dda0db4b5f2d9b7c3b93888c8c4bd857ffc0df","tid":2051590,"uid":358208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:11:39.